title: Counter-Strike 1.1 Full + Realbot
description:
Counter-Strike v1.1 v43 1006 Full Install

This is ripped from the retail version of Half-Life with all of the features in Counter-Strike v1.1. This version allows you to bhop with 2 speed setting adjustments.

fps_max 100
sv_airaccelerate 100
sv_maxspeed 10000

Bind your mousewheel to jump and you are set.

Also included are playable bots from RealBot, press the 'H' key to bring up the menu to add bots as a team or against them.

Remember to seed once you have finished downloading it.
